  <brief_title>co2 Gap and co2/o2 Ratio in Liver Transplant Patients</brief_title>
  <acronym>co2gap</acronym>
  <official_title>Use of the Venoarterial Carbon Dioxide Gap and Arteriovenous Oxygen Content to Guide the Resuscitation in the Liver Transplant Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
